name (-n) - the gene-set indicator i.e. xeno-iea
aspect (-a) - bp, mf, cc


## Create functionally coherent gene lists for biological process

(1) BLAST the reference genome (this only needs to be done once per assembly)
    ~$ python runBlast.py
    ~$ python runBlastParse.py
    ~$ python runBlastSummarize.py

(2) Create the term graph
    ~$ python createTermGraph.py -n name -a bp

(3) Calculate term distances
    ~$ python calculateTermDistances.py -n name -a bp
    ~$ python assembleDistances.py -n name -a bp

(4) Calculate gene distances
    ~$ python calculateGeneDistances.py -n name -a bp

(6) Run spectral clustering
    ~$ python spectralClusteringParamSearch.py -n -a bp
    ~$ python runSpectralClustering.py -n name -a bp

(8) Map names and assemble gene sets as gmt files
    ~$ 